{"tid":94502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"48cm陰莖男無法做愛？將成AV男優","createTime":"2017-01-25T09:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T03:52:20.000Z","uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8344436ca490492dc7d8b3a9bbe123a389b8cb11","tid":94502,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:08:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170125/420_2cbc2e4fd1d96ef8f749695d43ce56dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170125%2F420_2cbc2e4fd1d96ef8f749695d43ce56dc.jpg&h=82381ec9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n墨西哥男子卡布瑞拉(Roberto Esquivel Cabrera)擁有48.2公分陰莖，<span style=\"color: red;\">遠遠勝出高登會員號稱的「30公分」，但卡布瑞拉也因為擁有48公分大鵰，</span> 害他找不到合適的女性和他性交，生活作息也變得不方便，由於外型異於常人，他也沒辦法出去工作，甚至被政府認證是「殘障」。不過天生我材必有用，卡布瑞拉找到新工作，他將成為AV男優。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報導，「YouPorn」和「假計程車(Fake Taxi)」系列有興趣和54歲的卡布瑞拉合作，據悉YouPorn將安排卡布瑞拉拍攝醫護系列AV，安排一名「女醫生」和2~3名「護士」為卡布瑞拉「看診」。未來劇組人員也將會安排卡布瑞拉飛到布拉格拍攝，整支片子會以喜劇方式呈現，讓卡布瑞拉成為AV男優的初登場。<br />\n<br />\n目前美國的法肯(Jonah Falcon)是被認證的全世界最大雕，勃起前有24公分，勃起後達到34公分。卡布瑞拉相信自己已經超越這個數字，並希望申請金氏世界紀錄，但一直遲遲沒被批准。卡布瑞拉也承認，因為陽具太大影響了性生活，他曾經有2次做愛經驗，但第1位女性看到大鵰後被嚇跑，第2位女性則是做到一半，實在痛到受不了而作罷。<br />\n<br />\n不過卡布瑞拉也認為，自己也是因為巨大雕而讓世人認識他，他說：「<span style=\"color: red;\">其實我還蠻開心的，因為我的尺寸秒殺一堆人。</span> 」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170125/640_1cc68005fd12aec52e62c58c38ad9f00.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170125%2F640_1cc68005fd12aec52e62c58c38ad9f00.jpg&d=QfCtq%2FJ5M8ChdtAMCkZiHXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=d4a791a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170125/640_1cc68005fd12aec52e62c58c38ad9f00.jpg</a> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170125/420_334e23eb906da4e749a7674f12f4d7dc.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170125%2F420_334e23eb906da4e749a7674f12f4d7dc.jpg&d=QfCtq%2FJ5M8ChdtAMCkZiHXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=109240aa\" target=\"_blank\">http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170125/420_334e23eb906da4e749a7674f12f4d7dc.jpg</a> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170125/420_bf2a44ee4fc2458550c165eb5cd69559.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170125%2F420_bf2a44ee4fc2458550c165eb5cd69559.jpg&d=QfCtq%2FJ5M8ChdtAMCkZiHXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=833c24ea\" target=\"_blank\">http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170125/420_bf2a44ee4fc2458550c165eb5cd69559.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"3be37d66248e6a8124ccf39f050949bff5685790","tid":94502,"uid":1637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:25:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52872f14b5858701164c17f0356f6883a2d9f6b4","tid":94502,"uid":3502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:37:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b19585ece62f615af53d8d98cb52fb3bf9a0012","tid":94502,"uid":15877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:38:37.000Z","msg":"邊位巴打想比佢屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"988454c6556d028a1eec7e387a2d86746348d893","tid":94502,"uid":30044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:41:53.000Z","msg":"唔係話佢條j 有2/3係包皮咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb42861f0972be8f71f095893dad2ed8fa73c4b","tid":94502,"uid":61840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:50:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係話佢條j 有2/3係包皮咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clow